{"type":"answer","id":133553,"parentType":"question","parentId":15756,"uid":19469,"contents":"紅色是共產黨的顏色，象徵著暴力、鮮血、犯罪、恐怖主義、顛覆秩序。因此不用紅旗。<br>\n<br>\n黑色則象徵著中國人民要在被共匪玷污的地獄鬼國裡，成為光明之子的大軍，消滅共匪，光復中華。<br>\n<br>\n<a href=\"https://i.imgur.com/stiJokf.jpg\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/stiJokf.jpg\" alt=\"https://i.imgur.com/stiJokf.jpg\" style=\"max-width:100%\"></a>","date":"2020-01-21","agreeCount":6,"discussionCount":0}